To solve this problem, we need to show that the matchable sets of a graph $G$ form the independent sets of a matroid on $V(G)$, called the matchable sets matroid. We also need to prove that the rank of this matroid is $2\nu(G)$, where $\nu(G)$ is the maximum matching number of $G$.

