The rank of this matroid is $2 \cdot \nu(G)$, where $\nu(G)$ is the size of the maximum matching in $G$. This is because each edge in the matching contributes 2 to the sum of the sizes of the matchings, and the maximum matching will have size $\nu(G)$. 

